App verbs for Mattermost plugin contract (fulcrum apps v5.10.1)

USAGE fulcrum apps [OPTIONS] list|get|deploy|stop|rollback|logs

OPTIONS

     --port    Server port (default: 7777)                                          
      --url    Override full server URL                                             
  --no-json    Emit JSON envelope (default and only output mode for plugin contract)
    --debug    Show detailed error stack traces                                     

COMMANDS

      list    List apps                        
       get    Get a single app                 
    deploy    Trigger a deployment             
      stop    Stop an app                      
  rollback    Rollback to a previous deployment
      logs    Fetch service logs               

Use fulcrum apps <command> --help for more information about a command.


